properties.name: dataset
properties.comment: A DOMString representing the value of the id attribute on the given element, or the empty string if id is not present.

properties.name: xmlBase
properties.comment: A DOMString corresponding to the xml:base attribute on the given element.

properties.name: ownerSVGElement
properties.comment: An SVGSVGElement referring to the nearest ancestor <svg> element. null if the given element is the outermost <svg> element.

properties.name: viewportElement
properties.comment: The SVGElement, which established the current viewport. Often, the nearest ancestor <svg> element. null if the given element is the outermost <svg> element.
